DOC.brief_summary: This post-marketing, multi-center prospective study will be conducted in a open-label, non-interventional setting, for women seeking fertility treatment and will describe morphokinetic de-selection parameters in human embryos.
DOC.brief_title: An Explorative Prospective Observational Study to Describe Morphokinetic De-selection Parameters in Human Embryos
DOC.criteria: Age 2145 years In Vitro Fertilisation/Intra Cytoplasmic Sperm Injection treatment in long or short protocol Receiving follicle stimulation with Menopur 600/1200 IU
